
During the working with the enviroment please note that the following variables
are available

BUILDER_ROOT - The path of the tbuilder
BUILDER_NAME - tbuilder
PROJECT_NAME - the name of the project
SOURCES	     - the name of the sources folder
TEST_DIR     - the name of the sources folder
DEV_ROOT        the path of the development root, that is the folder where is 
                the SOURCES directory
PREFIX       - the path where should be created the binary files
